.br
.RS

.RE
.SH FUNCTIONS
.LP
.B
\fBgetFiles(This) -> [unicode:charlist()]\fR
\fB                  when This :: wxDropFilesEvent().\fR

.br
.RS
.PP
Returns an array of filenames.


.RE
.B
\fBgetNumberOfFiles(This) -> integer()\fR
\fB                          when This :: wxDropFilesEvent().\fR

.br
.RS
.PP
Returns the number of files dropped.


.RE
.B
\fBgetPosition(This) -> {X :: integer(), Y :: integer()}\fR
\fB                     when This :: wxDropFilesEvent().\fR

.br
.RS
.PP
Returns the position at which the files were dropped.

.PP
